        {
            "title": "青衣長康邨單位闢私煙倉 海關檢$18萬私煙 六旬獨居漢被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/510102887590807126c2de418a72b375/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031021511075692.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>海關今日（10日）下午於青衣進行反私煙活動，期間於長康邨截查一名可疑男子，在他攜帶的行李箱及環保袋內，搜獲少量懷疑私煙。人員隨即將他押返邨內一單位的住所調查，並在該個面積約200呎的小型單位內，檢獲多3萬支私煙，於是拘捕該名68歲無業漢。\n\n</p>\n<p>行動中，海關檢獲約4萬支私煙，市值約18萬元，應課稅值約13萬元，相信疑犯利用公屋單位作私煙儲存倉庫，並將私煙售予區內用家，每賣出一條私煙，可賺取100多元報酬。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4130153/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關拘捕一名68歲無業漢。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/655ec7b004af5a55c77b29bef409cff0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_195528129.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關拘捕一名68歲無業漢。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4130154/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關拘捕一名68歲無業漢。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/287218ced57f23ce860528404bb1e783/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_195527036.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關拘捕一名68歲無業漢。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4130155/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲約4萬支私煙，市值約18萬元，應課稅值約13萬元。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/607e04a4d2bafd1e4ceb5e335401fa55/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_195525677.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲約4萬支私煙，市值約18萬元，應課稅值約13萬元。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4130156/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲約4萬支私煙，市值約18萬元，應課稅值約13萬元。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b98d3b4ee91da839a1cdc45dfa8fb9f1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_195520988.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲約4萬支私煙，市值約18萬元，應課稅值約13萬元。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4130157/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲約4萬支私煙，市值約18萬元，應課稅值約13萬元。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec77606f63026897647b90b2f1b4603f/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_195519228.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲約4萬支私煙，市值約18萬元，應課稅值約13萬元。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
