        {
            "title": "藍田麗港城校服少女過路 遭的士撞倒腳傷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"藍田麗港城校服少女過路 遭的士撞倒腳傷送院。FB：麗港城討論區\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b022a38ddac38a5580104fcf527e04aa/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031021310881454.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">藍田麗港城校服少女過路 遭的士撞倒腳傷送院。FB：麗港城討論區</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（3月10日）晚上約9時，觀塘茶果嶺道99號麗港城，一名50多歲的士司機，行駛至一過路處時，撞倒一名10多歲過路校服少女。\n\n</p>\n<p>少女腳部受傷，其他途人大驚報案。救護員接報趕至，將其送往聯合醫院治理。意外原因仍在調查。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057398/即時-港聞-藍田麗港城校服少女過路-遭的士撞倒腳傷送院",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 21:31:42",
