            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Ian抵達倫敦過百Hellosss接機  親切揮手打招呼回應粉絲支持",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Ian在英國時間早上6時平安抵達倫敦。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/581e6f91e2c5884f9113112b6ee683b9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031021211932033.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Ian在英國時間早上6時平安抵達倫敦。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>陳卓賢（lan）首個海外巡迴演唱會《IAN CHAN \"TEARS\" IN MY SIGHT SOLO CONCERT 2025》 將於3月13日於倫敦 OVO Arena Wembley展開序幕。昨晚（9日）Ian乘坐國泰航空啟程出發到倫敦，大批粉絲Hellosss（粉絲暱稱）到場送機。15小時後，Ian在英國時間早上6時平安抵達倫敦，過百英國Hellosss們亦一早到達機場守候迎接偶像，場面墟冚。\n\n</p><h2>Hellosss開心近距離迎接偶像</h2>\n<p>Ian及團隊於早上7:15步出入境大堂，過百名Hellosss即手持燈牌橫額列隊歡呼，現實秩序良好，Ian身穿深啡外套白色cap帽，在多名保安人員護送下慢慢走過fans接機區，途中他親切地與Hellosss揮手及點頭打招呼，眾Hellosss近距離迎接偶像，心情興奮難奈，期間當有人大叫「Good Show」及「加油」時，Ian也會向他們點頭回應，而步出機場前，Ian亦特意回頭揮手講拜拜。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"過百英國Hellosss們亦一早到達機場守候迎接偶像，場面墟冚。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1cd6373614c8941ecae79aee71cb7bf7/2025-03/IMG-20250310-WA0046.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        過百英國Hellosss們亦一早到達機場守候迎接偶像，場面墟冚。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian及團隊於早上7:15步出入境大堂。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df6da0776580f1642b7ed051e5d30699/2025-03/IMG-20250310-WA0047.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian及團隊於早上7:15步出入境大堂。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"途中他親切地與Hellosss揮手及點頭打招呼\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e55876ca20111f0256918f6533d08fe3/2025-03/IMG-20250310-WA0048.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        途中他親切地與Hellosss揮手及點頭打招呼\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"眾Hellosss近距離迎接偶像，心情興奮難奈。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3296a20b5d5d9b63d426b784bf813f8/2025-03/IMG-20250310-WA0049.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        眾Hellosss近距離迎接偶像，心情興奮難奈。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian身穿深啡外套白色cap帽，在多名保安人員護送下慢慢走過fans接機區，\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/30fffebd12a6c316af8e0ec900ad3e49/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1017_08_08_44c3e99e.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian身穿深啡外套白色cap帽，在多名保安人員護送下慢慢走過fans接機區，\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"期間當有人大叫「Good Show」及「加油」時，Ian也會向他們點頭回應。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c13f293546c58514840145bc119799f/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1017_08_08_fe410159.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        期間當有人大叫「Good Show」及「加油」時，Ian也會向他們點頭回應。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>金廣城亦有隨行支持Ian</h2>\n<p>昨晚Ian透露倫敦演唱會會有新歌單及編排，小背心show肌環節隨時準備好，更預告有新造型及小驚喜。雖然自己都有點緊張，但團隊準備功夫十足，Ian請大家拭目以待，期望可以帶給觀眾極盡視聽之娛的精彩演出。Viu 製作部副總裁金廣城亦有隨行欣賞MIRROR首位成員單飛巡唱，支持十足。預祝Ian 2025世界巡迴演唱會成功。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
